6" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4-686x580.jpeg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/0e91e798951fe2c34fe4.jpeg 1052w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/xiaomi-15-ultra/mobile-phone/">小米 15 Ultra 发表: 首部支持奥斯卡 ACES 电影色彩系统 Android 手机</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
